      • createTransaction

        public void createTransaction(Item item,
                              double updatedBudget)

        Override of createTransaction method of IView, after the the validation that the transaction can be done we call the createTransaction method of CostManagerView, this method will call createTransaction method of addItemsPage and will add the new item to the database of the user and will update the wallet balance of the user.

        Specified by:
        createTransaction in interface IView
        Parameters:
        item - Contains the item that the user wishes to add to the database.
        updatedBudget - The amount we need to deduct from the user's wallet.
